, at high altitudes (
<quantity id="4C943D922C7FF453937FF84CF5A6F7B3" box="[838,988,2025,2049]" metricMagnitude="3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="3.8649999999999998" metricValueMax="3.9899999999999998" metricValueMin="3.7399999999999998" pageId="14" pageNumber="117" unit="m" value="3865.0" valueMax="3990.0" valueMin="3740.0">3740–3990 m</quantity>
). The specimens bearing labels indicating
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BD390772C7EF45290AEFF4CF76BFEF3" blockId="15.[151,756,233,321]" pageId="15" pageNumber="118">
Emei Shan as the locality of collection were most likely mislabeled; for additional comments see the section on 
